title: Cheryl Cole Goes Public With Her Pregnancy, Debuts Baby Bump in Tight Black Dress
text: Cheryl Cole Goes Public With Her Pregnancy, Debuts Baby Bump in Tight Black Dress by Zach Seemayer 8:33   After months of speculation , Cheryl Cole is showing off her sizeable baby bump! In a publicity photo for L'Oreal Paris' partnership with The Prince's Trust -- first published by The Mirror U.K. -- the 33-year-old X Factor U.K. judge can be seen rocking a skin-tight black dress, and standing in profile to put her growing bump on display. Tomorrow's Daily Mirror front page: From rags to Â£14m Lotto riches.. #tomorrowspaperstoday https://t.co/oxkRxudjbH pic.twitter.com/ypJr72Zr4y WATCH: Liam Payne Expecting a Baby With Cheryl Cole? See the Pic That Has Everyone Talking! Rumors that Cole and her boyfriend, One Direction singer Liam Payne, were expecting a child together first popped up in November when the couple attended the Fayre of St. James' charity Christmas concert in London, England. Cole and Payne, 23, walked the red carpet together, where the "Call My Name" singer wore a curve-hugging olive green dress, which appeared to hint at a growing baby bump. Photo: Getty Images PHOTOS: Celeb Pregnancy Style The pair have still not publicly addressed the pregnancy news, though Cole proudly displaying her pregnant belly seems to be a sweetly simple confirmation. The couple first met in 2008 when Payne auditioned for The X Factor U.K. , but they didn't officially begin dating until last February, and have been navigating recurring and persistent pregnancy rumors since nearly the beginning of their relationship. WATCH: Liam Payne and Cheryl Cole Reveal New 'Family Member' -- Meet Their New Puppy! In December, Payne took part in an #AskLiam Twitter Q&A, and while he avoided directly answering fans' questions about whether or not he and Cole were expecting a child, Payne boasted that he's "the happiest I could be."
